com.force.sdk.test.util
Class UserInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.force.sdk.test.util.UserInfo

public class UserInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Immutable set of user information that allows to establish context for this user and retrieve any additional information. This is NOT a minimal set of information. Changes to this class, i.e. addition of user information should be added to the equals implementation.
